Module RoboRally
Package utils.json

Class MessageDistributer

  • java.lang.Object
    • utils.json.MessageDistributer
  • public class MessageDistributer
extends java.lang.Object
    This class has the sole purpose to distribute the logic for each JSONMessage into seperate functions that are called when the corresponding message was deserialized.

      • handleHelloServer

        public void handleHelloServer​(Server server,
                              Server.ServerReaderTask task,
                              HelloServerBody helloServerBody)
        This method contains the logic that comes into action when a 'HelloServer' protocol message was received and deserialized by the Server. It is triggered by ClientMessageAction.triggerAction(Server, Server.ServerReaderTask, Object, MessageDistributer).
        Parameters:
        server - The Server itself.
        task - The ReaderTask of the distributerServer (Gives access to the PrintWriter).
        helloServerBody - The message body of the message which is of type HelloServerBody.
